article.description: Cassius Winston had 19 points and seven assists to help No. 11 Michigan State cruise past No. 17 UCLA 87-67 on Thursday night to reach the final of the Las Vegas Invitational.
article.headline: No. 11 Michigan State easily beats No. 17 UCLA
article.linkText: No. 11 Michigan State easily beats No. 17 UCLA
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- Cassius Winston had 19 points and seven assists to help No. 11 Michigan State cruise past No. 17 UCLA 87-67 on Thursday night to reach the final of the Las Vegas Invitational. Nick Ward scored 16 points, Joshua Langford had 14 and Josh McQuaid had 11 for Michigan State (4-1). The Spartans will play Texas in the championship game Friday. The Bruins (4-1) take on No. 7 North Carolina in the consolation game. Texas stunned the Tar Heels earlier Thursday, 92-89. Kris Wilkes had 15 points to lead UCLA. Jaylen Hands and Chris Smith each had 11 points for the Bruins, who shot 36 percent from the field. Michigan State shot 52 percent from the field and led throughout, building a 29-point lead with 1:49 until halftime. The Spartans shot 10 of 17 from 3-point range in the session, while UCLA shot 24 percent.

videos.headline: Ward runs the floor for easy dunk
videos.description: Nick Ward runs the floor for the Spartans and gets an easy dunk in transition.

videos.headline: Winston knocks down the and-1 from deep
videos.description: Cassius Winston draws the foul on the 3-point shot and sinks the bucket.

videos.headline: Winston sinks smooth step-through floater
videos.description: Cassius Winston uses a fake and then a step-through move to hit a smooth floater in the lane in transition.

videos.headline: Langford gets swirling 3-pointer to fall
videos.description: Joshua Langford takes a 3-pointer in the corner and it takes a few swirls around the rim until it finally goes down.

videos.headline: Winston hits off-balance floater off glass
videos.description: Cassisus Winston draws three defenders and kisses a difficult floater high off the glass while drifting toward the baseline.

videos.headline: Brown gets nice chase-down block
videos.description: Moses Brown gets a nice chase-down block on the fast break and ferociously throws it off the backboard.
